<div><div><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex">
Process migration was implemented in Open MPI and working in the trunk a couple of years ago. It has not been well maintained for a few years though (hopefully that will change one day). So you can try it, but your results may vary.<div>



